name: "多国汇率小组件"
description: "在桌面小组件中实时展示美元、欧元、英镑、日元(100)、港币对人民币的汇率"
author: "zpiz"

scriptings:
  - generic:
      name: "multi-exchange-rate"
      # 这里需要替换为你实际存放 js 脚本的远程 URL 或本地路径
      script_url: "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/zpiz/scripts/refs/heads/main/Egern/exchange-rate.js" 
      timeout: 10

widgets:
  # 在模块中直接声明小组件，启用模块后自动生效
  - name: "multi-exchange-rate"
